  }, "Everyone is dealt a hand at the start\u2026"), mdx("p", null, "The starting line of us humans is different; the world is not fair. I am glad that I wasn\u2019t born somewhere in Africa, but I still live in a relatively well-developed country called Slovakia, and I do not miss anything extraordinary. Even though my parents didn\u2019t have a lot of money, I had access to education, and later it was up to me what to do next. Sure, there are circumstances we can\u2019t control. But we can still change a lot of things if we are motivated enough. It\u2019s very similar to computer games."), mdx("h2", {
